OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775319067
OL,3,CWoman jailed for defrauding GP surgery
OL,4,Cof more than #450k
OL,6,FA woman has been jailed for more than
OL,7,Fthree years after fraudulently
OL,8,Fdiverting almost half a million pounds
OL,9,Ffrom a GP surgery in Berkshire.
OL,11,F43 year old Lauren Millington from
OL,12,FHook in Hampshire, was sentenced to
OL,13,Fthree years and two months in prison
OL,14,Fat Reading Crown Court on 1 April.
OL,16,FRoger Happe, 44, from Egham, was also
OL,17,Fgiven a nine month prison sentence,
OL,18,Fsuspended for two years, and ordered
OL,19,Fto complete 100 hours of community
OL,20,Fservice.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
