FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775319067
OL,3,CWoman jailed for defrauding GP surgery
OL,4,Cof more than #450k
OL,6,FMillington admitted two counts of
OL,7,Ffraud by abuse of position and one
OL,8,Fcount of concealing criminal property.
OL,9,FHappe pleaded guilty to acquiring and
OL,10,Fpossessing criminal property.
OL,12,FBetween February 2021 and November
OL,13,F2024, Millington worked as a finance
OL,14,Fmanager at The Waterfield Practice in
OL,15,FBracknell. During that time, she
OL,16,Fdiverted #456,666 from the surgery.
OL,18,FAn investigation by Thames Valley
OL,19,FPolice began after the practice raised
OL,20,Fconcerns about suspicious payments to
OL,21,Fexternal medical suppliers.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775319067
OL,3,CWoman jailed for defrauding GP surgery
OL,4,Cof more than #450k
OL,6,FOfficers found legitimate banking
OL,7,Fdetails for several companies had been
OL,8,Faltered so payments were redirected
OL,9,Finto accounts controlled by Millington.
OL,11,FA further #25,190 was paid into an
OL,12,Faccount belonging to Happe. Both were
OL,13,Farrested in January 2025 and later
OL,14,Fcharged in December that year.
OL,16,FDetective Constable Jagdip Sekhon, of
OL,17,Fthe Berkshire Volume Fraud Team,
OL,18,Fdescribed the offending as "calculated
OL,19,Fand sustained," involving fake
OL,20,Finvoices and the manipulation of
OL,21,Fcompany systems.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775319067
OL,3,CWoman jailed for defrauding GP surgery
OL,4,Cof more than #450k
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Duncan Wynn, head
OL,7,Fof the Central Fraud Unit, said
OL,8,FMillington "systematically abused" her
OL,9,Fposition, leaving a "hole in much
OL,10,Fneeded public finances." He added the
OL,11,Fpractice had been left with a
OL,12,Fsignificant shortfall in funds
OL,13,Fintended to support the local
OL,14,Fcommunity.
OL,16,FThames Valley Police said the case
OL,17,Fdemonstrates its commitment to
OL,18,Fbringing fraudsters to justice.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
